Julie Gibson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Julie_Gibson 0 Julie Gibson (born September 6, 1913) is an American former singer and actress who had a prolific film career during the 1940s.Gibson is Hollywood's oldest known living performer from the "Golden Age".
